input: Abstract: The new "GeoBERT" model is presented, offering groundbreaking outcomes in geospatial data interpretation. In contrast, existing solutions like "GeoSentimentNet" are limited in processing multilingual datasets. We also benchmark against "SpatialTransformer" and "GeoMLP" to validate performance enhancements. The experimental results depict GeoBERTâ€™s exceptional ability over "GeoSentimentNet".
